# Paths Prettier must not touch. Lockfile, build output, coverage output, mutation reports, changeset queue. All machine-authored. Re-formatting them would cause spurious diffs on every install / build / test / mutation / version run; re-formatting the lockfile corrupts it.

pnpm-lock.yaml
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/coverage/
**/reports/
**/.changeset/
